review.reviewBody: such great food and a good price! Cheesecake is amazing Butter Paneer Pizza Veggie Samosa  were some of the best I have had.

Personal Butter Chicken or Paneer Comes with Rice, Butter Naan & Caesar Salad 
very small portion(perfect for a small child), with only 4 tiny chucks  of chicken and  was not very good didnt even taste good. salad was warm and soaky amd the  naan bread was 1 piece cut into 4s and  hard and cold.
price was 14.99 and i ended up paying 26.00 after all said and done for delivery.              BullS**t !!!!!
will NOT be ordering from here AGAIN!!
Is it cheap? Yeah kinda. Is the food good? Not really. Would I order from here again? Probably not.

Overall, I wouldnt order again from Rosie's based off my experience, and I also wouldn't recommend it for other customers. 

1. I received the wrong pizza. I ordered a cheese pizza but instead received a meat pizza. 

2. I ordered the Personal Butter Chicken or Paneer Comes with Rice, Butter Naan & Caesar Salad. The butter chicken itself is almost 50% oil, the sauce should not be made of such a high oil content. The taste of the sauce itself is actually good but it's so saturated in oil it ruins the entire dish, the flavour was one of two reasons I gave it two stars. The sides were as expected.
